longBusinessSummary: GetFugu, Inc. develops mobile search tools and mobile e-commerce platform. The company's application tools allow consumers to retrieve content and eliminate the need to type Website addresses or search terms into the mobile devices' Internet browser. It offers agnostic mobile search platform. The company was formerly known as Madero, Inc. and changed its name to GetFugu, Inc. in March 2009. GetFugu, Inc. was founded in 2007 and is based in West Hollywood, California.
